<h1>轻</h1><p class=neha><span style="color:#990000;">qīng</span><span class=alesi>(qing1)</span> <span class=lesi>// pronunciation of 轻 in Mandarin Pinyin</span></p><h2>Basic information about 轻</h2><div class=abo>
